      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TOBY KEEPING (7) shapes well for this backing up a lightning 22.44 win with success at Angle Park over 530m last time, recording 30.81. Smart win two back and looks a key chance here. SON OF MAPLE (1) has a strong record this track and trip with two wins and three placings from six starts. In the money last time at Murray Bridge (22.66) in a Special conditions race, finishing a 5 length second. Looks suited here and can measure up. CRAZED (3) slotted in just off the lead from the wide draw last start and boxed on to finish second (22.95) at Gawler in a Other over 400m. Hard to beat again. YARRAMUNDI OPAL (5) generally performs well over this distance.",
